questions.question: How to register?
questions.answer: To register, click on the 'Register' button in the top right corner and follow the instructions.

questions.question: How to find matches?
questions.answer: Our algorithm will find the most suitable matches based on your interests.

questions.question: How to contact support?
questions.answer: You can contact our support through the feedback form on the 'Contact' page.

questions.question: How to change my profile picture?
questions.answer: Go to your profile settings and click on 'Change Profile Picture'.

questions.question: How to delete my account?
questions.answer: You can delete your account in the account settings section.
